bool Slic3r::GUI::Plater::open_3mf_file ( const fs::path &  file_path)
9297{
9298 std::string filename = encode_path(file_path.filename().string().c_str());
9299 if (!boost::algorithm::iends_with(filename, ".3mf")) {
9300 return false;
9301 }
9302
9303 LoadType load_type = LoadType::Unknown;
9304 if (!model().objects.empty()) {
9305 bool show_drop_project_dialog = true;
9306 if (show_drop_project_dialog) {
9307 ProjectDropDialog dlg(filename);
9308 if (dlg.ShowModal() == wxID_OK) {
9309 int choice = dlg.get_action();
9310 load_type = static_cast<LoadType>(choice);
9311 wxGetApp().app_config->set("import_project_action", std::to_string(choice));
9312
9313 // BBS: jump to plater panel
9314 wxGetApp().mainframe->select_tab(MainFrame::tp3DEditor);
9315 }
9316 } else
9317 load_type = static_cast<LoadType>(
9318 std::clamp(std::stoi(wxGetApp().app_config->get("import_project_action")), static_cast<int>(LoadType::OpenProject), static_cast<int>(LoadType::LoadConfig)));
9319 } else
9320 load_type = LoadType::OpenProject;
9321
9322 if (load_type == LoadType::Unknown) return false;
9323
9324 switch (load_type) {
9325 case LoadType::OpenProject: {
9326 if (wxGetApp().can_load_project())
9327 load_project(from_path(file_path));
9328 break;
9329 }
9330 case LoadType::LoadGeometry: {
9331 Plater::TakeSnapshot snapshot(this, "Import Object");
9332 load_files({file_path}, LoadStrategy::LoadModel);
9333 break;
9334 }
9335 case LoadType::LoadConfig: {
9336 load_files({file_path}, LoadStrategy::LoadConfig);
9337 break;
9338 }
9339 case LoadType::Unknown: {
9340 assert(false);
9341 break;
9342 }
9343 }
9344
9345 return true;
9346}
